.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
There 5 different types of food: banana, raspberry, cauliflower, grapefruit, lime
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, daffodil, balloon-flower, dahlia
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the person eating banana is the person who likes red
2. the person eating raspberry is the owner of the dog
3. the person who growspoppy is the person who likes green
4. the person eating cauliflower is the person who growssunflower
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the old-gold-smoker is the owner of the snails
7. the kools-smoker is the person who likes yellow
8. the person who growsdaffodil is in the middle
9. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person who growsballoon-flower
13. the person eating lime is the parliaments-smoker
14. the person eating grapefruit is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Food	|   grapefruit	|    cauliflower	|     banana	|    raspberry	|    lime	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Flower	|     dahlia	|      sunflower	|      daffodil	| balloon-flower	|     poppy	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
